    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward, and priced to move, this vehicle offers practical transportation for a budget-conscious buyer. It shows age and wear consistent with an older used car, but presents a solid opportunity for someone seeking dependable basic mobility without a big upfront cost. A sensible choice for a commuter, first-time driver, or backup vehicle.",
