      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true under-the-radar find with tons of personality, this car offers an honest, broken-in charm that\u2019s hard to fake. It has the kind of presence that invites a second look and the kind of potential that makes it perfect for someone who appreciates a vehicle with a story to tell. Whether you\u2019re after an inexpensive daily, a weekend tinkering project, or simply a practical set of wheels with character, this one delivers a lot of opportunity at a wallet-friendly price.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
