      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or daily candidate with a strong-running powertrain, responsive automatic transmission, and dependable start-up behavior. This car shows cosmetic wear and age consistent with a well-used vehicle, but it still offers good utility with stable road manners, usable cabin space, and straightforward mechanicals that make it an appealing option for someone who wants affordable transportation or a hands-on fixer-upper. A practical buy for the money with plenty of serviceable life left for the next owner.",
